headline: Kratos Defense Q3 Earnings Top Estimates, Revenues Rise Y/Y
summary: KTOS' third-quarter 2024 revenues of $275.9 million miss the Zacks Consensus Estimate by 0.9%. The figure, however, rises 0.5% from the year-ago level.
